opera jawa ( requiem from java ) is a 2006 indonesian-austrian musical film directed by garin nugroho that features traditional javanese classical music and dance in a setting of opera that is inspired by the " abduction of sita " episode from the ramayana .   the film was commissioned for peter sellars ' new crowned hope festival in celebration of the 250th anniversary of the birth of wolfgang amadeus mozart .   in addition to music by rahayu supanggah , the film features installation art production design by nanang rhamat .